{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5d51fb6166","title":"毛泽东四点指示（张春桥传达）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ef6e97a47c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":17,"articleId":"5d51fb6166"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"471a503675","name":"张春桥","type":"人物"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dd96f8fdf2","type":"title","text":"四点指示（张春桥传达）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d51fb6166"},{"id":"4fabf5d925","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d51fb6166"},{"id":"c14397b269","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）今年搞文化大革命的指导思想是《红旗》和《人民日报》元旦社论，展开全面的阶级斗争。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d51fb6166"},{"id":"38f829e441","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）要抓四个重点：北京、上海、天津、东北。责任是在造反派身上，要团结多数，造反派队伍要超过一倍以上。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d51fb6166"},{"id":"8572fb3625","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）上海很有希望，许多学生、工人、机关干部起来了，这是当前文化大革命的形势。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d51fb6166"},{"id":"89130fb7c4","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）红卫兵要向解放军学习，一定要朴素。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d51fb6166"},{"id":"ffaf02872a","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥还说：毛主席在元旦祝酒时说：“祝你们明年过社会主义关。”","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d51fb6166"}],"page":{"id":"4585be622e","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5d51fb6166","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}